bes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142722.506-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142722.506.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" data-id=\"12841\"  src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142711.352-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12841\" srcset=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142711.352-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142711.352-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142711.352-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-03-14T142711.352.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;I like our village, I like our weather and we all live with unity but not having water makes everyday life difficult for many of our households. We also live very far from the nearest hospital and the roads are terrible. We use solar energy as we are not connected to any power lines, but this can be difficult during the rainy season. We also need it at night, so storing and keeping enough is not simple. \u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>I am hoping that we can connect our village to others. Maybe we can find markets to sell our produce and some agencies that work with farmers.&#8221; <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Supporting villages like Huay Mai Dam is often an important step in providing a foundation of development and improving basic needs. This allows villages to think beyond the everyday struggles and focus on improving their lives in other ways, either related to livelihoods, education or other improvements. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"http:\/\/www.karenhilltribes.org.uk\/donate\">donate<\/a> to support our WASH Systems and you can also follow our social media and share this post to help us reach more people! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>KHT&#8217;s Water and Sanitation Systems not only provide&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":12838,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.12 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Making Life Better in Ban Huay Mai Dam - Karen Hilltribes Trust<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/making-life-better-in-ban-huay-mai-dam\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Making Life Better in Ban Huay Mai Dam - Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"KHT&#8217;s Water and Sanitation Systems not only provide...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/making-life-better-in-ban-huay-mai-dam\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2023-03-14T15:34:29+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2023-03-14T15:34:31+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/MicrosoftTeams-image-100.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image